item.title: Goodbye 2020 - New Year's cards for 2021
item.description: Every year, FC and I make Christmas or New Year’s cards. Looking back, our 2020 was so dominated by the Coronavirus to the extent that not much else were there to talk about. Our only memorable part of last year was the summer months between the 1st wave and the 2nd wave of the outbreak, when the situation was relatively peaceful and we had two short trips to the Mediterranean Sea.
